00:02:23.200 --> 00:02:31.060
So, I mean, marginally, let's say just for the sake

00:02:31.060 --> 00:02:33.240
of notation, I'm going to think of a function of three

00:02:33.240 --> 00:02:38.220
variables xyz where the variables are related by some

00:02:38.220 --> 00:02:42.940
equation, but they will put a form in the form g of xyz

