There is actually a formula, but that formula is quite

00:04:44.920 --> 00:04:45.500
complicated.

00:04:45.660 --> 00:04:46.920
We actually don't want to do that.

00:04:47.180 --> 00:04:47.920
That's an easier way.

00:04:56.060 --> 00:04:57.580
So, how can we do it?

00:04:57.960 --> 00:05:02.000
Well, let's look at the differential.

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:10.120
Of this constraint quantity.

00:05:10.740 --> 00:05:14.340
So, if we call this g, let's look at dg.

00:05:18.700 --> 00:05:21.000
So, well, what's the differential of this?

00:05:21.740 --> 00:05:29.520
So, differential of x squared is 2x dx plus, I think,

