when we have variables that are related.

00:19:41.560 --> 00:19:43.700
Because let's say now that I have a function

00:19:43.700 --> 00:19:46.740
that depends on x, y, and z, but x, y, and z are related.

00:19:47.620 --> 00:19:49.960
Then it means that, you know,

00:19:50.880 --> 00:19:55.420
if I look at, say, x and y as my independent variables

